口述实录 | 30小时从美返沪亲历三大国际机场，上海严出真情。
Running back to Shanghai from the US for three major international airports in 30 hours, Shanghai is sobering.
李 莹。
Li Ying.
新民周刊                      。
Xinmin Weekly.
新民周刊。
Xinmin Weekly.
深度和角度——这就是我们能做的。
Depth and angle - that's what we can do.
